## Integration with Session Continuation

When token threshold reached:
1. Show warning (this rule)
2. Trigger session-continuation skill (if available)
3. Save workflow state to `.cursor/workflow-contexts/`
4. Provide resume instructions

**See:** `.cursor/rules/skills/auto-invoke/session-continuation/session-management.md` (if exists)

